'''''Arende''''', ni Sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo 1994 iyobowe na Dirk de Villiers .   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Ian Roberts na Gavin van den Berg mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Diane Wilson, Keith Grenville na Percy Sieff mu nshingano zabo. 

Iyi filime ivuga ibyerekeranye n’Intambara ya Anglo Boer nubuzima bwumuhinzi wigometse Boer Sloet Steenkamp na Kapiteni wingabo [[Ubwongereza|zUbwongereza]] James Kerwin.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime. 

